OL,3,CNursery shuts temporarily due to staff
OL,4,Cshortages
OL,6,FA Jersey early years provider has
OL,7,Ftemporarily shut its doors due to
OL,8,Fstaff shortages.
OL,10,FThe Jersey Leeward Nursery, run by
OL,11,FBusy Bees near Springfield Stadium in
OL,12,FSt Helier, says there is not enough
OL,13,Fqualified staff to allow it to operate
OL,14,Fsafely.
OL,16,FThe nursery is closed completely on
OL,17,FFriday 25 July and will then run a
OL,18,Freduced operation for the following
OL,19,Ftwo weeks to "allow for training and
OL,20,Fto maintain required child and staff
OL,21,Fratios".
