OL,3,CNursery shuts temporarily due to staff
OL,4,Cshortages
OL,6,FBusy Bees adds that while they are
OL,7,Ftrying to move staff to provide cover,
OL,8,Ftheir sister nurseries are operating
OL,9,Fnear capacity and there are already
OL,10,Fchallenges with it being the peak
OL,11,Fholiday season.
OL,13,FThey state: "For some time, we have
OL,14,Fbeen trying to manage a shortage of
OL,15,Fappropriately qualified team members
OL,16,Fat our Jersey Leeward Nursery.
OL,18,F"Whilst being proactive in trying to
OL,19,Frecruit new team members and drawing
OL,20,Fupon staff from our sister nurseries,
OL,21,Fthe situation has been challenging.
