OL,3,CNursery shuts temporarily due to staff
OL,4,Cshortages
OL,6,F"We are very grateful for the
OL,7,Fpatience, understanding and
OL,8,Fflexibility shown by our families as
OL,9,Fwe work our way through this."
OL,11,FBusy Bees says they are working on
OL,12,Ftraining and upskilling staff so they
OL,13,Fcan cover more roles, while
OL,14,Ftemporarily bringing over other
OL,15,Femployees from the UK to fill the
OL,16,Fshortfall in expertise.
