OL,3,CNursery shuts temporarily due to staff
OL,4,Cshortages
OL,6,FThey explain: "The staff team are
OL,7,Fworking incredibly hard, and we
OL,8,Fappreciate the support they have
OL,9,Freceived from parents who have been
OL,10,Funderstanding of the challenges the
OL,11,Fteam faces.
OL,13,F"We recognise the impact this
OL,14,Fsituation has upon our families and
OL,15,Fhave apologised to them for the
OL,16,Finconvenience and upset this has
OL,17,Fcaused.
