OL,3,CNursery shuts temporarily due to staff
OL,4,Cshortages
OL,6,F"Where we have been unable to provide
OL,7,Fa place for a child due to staff
OL,8,Fshortages, we will be providing a full
OL,9,Frefund for any days missed and will
OL,10,Fcontinue to update our families on the
OL,11,Fprogress of our plan."
OL,13,FThe nursery aims to reopen fully from
OL,14,FMonday 11 August.
OL,16,FThe Government of Jersey adds: "The
OL,17,FChildcare and Early Years Service
OL,18,F(CEYS) continues to closely support
OL,19,Fthe nursery.
